

> ./make_superlink  sim.out.ped sim.out.ped.sl

> ./make_locus_files.pl 4 sim.rec_rates sim.haps locus.
#./make_locus_files.pl $num_sites $rec_rates $haps locus.



To run Merlin's non-parametric linkage analysis:
------------------------------------------------

Download merlin to this directory and install so that it is located at "merlin-1.1.2/merlin"

> ./run_merlin.pl 4 sim.out.ped sim.rec_rates sim.out.ped.merlin

> cat sim.out.ped.merlin
gives the LOD scores for each of the SNPs